text: Waikato is an electorate in the New Zealand Parliament. A Waikato electorate was first created in 1871 and an electorate by this name has existed from 1871 to 1963, 1969 to 1996, and 2008 to the present, though exact borders have often changed. ==Election results== ==References== Category:New Zealand electorates
title: Waikato (New Zealand electorate)
